The package boost-local-function is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS local_function)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::local_function)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_local_function REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::local_function)
